properties.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in the Lyons Gate Community. Upgraded kitchen cabinets, gas appliances, granite counter tops, Brand New Upgraded Carpet, gorgeous wood like tile throughout downstairs, surround sound, two car garage, covered back patio, professionally paved backyard, large master bedroom, master bathroom with dual vanities and large walk-in closet are just a few of the features/upgrades that this home includes. With no yard-work required, you'll have plenty of time to take advantage of all of the amenities this community has to offer, including: basketball courts, large playground, grassy common areas, dog park, and a community pool/spa. Come check it out!
